(19, 1, '2018-03-09 10:00:04', '2018-03-09 10:00:04', '<div class="inner-content">\r\n<div class="f-l">\r\n<div id="content">\r\n<h1>Sponsorship Opportunities</h1>\r\nThe <strong>CEE Capital Markets &amp; FinTech Awards</strong> offers you the opportunity to market your business and build image awareness as well as gain maximum exposure by becoming a sponsor of the event.\r\n\r\nThe Awards Gala and Summit combines a professional daytime Summit covering key issues for CEE''s capital-markets sector with rich networking opportunities at the evening Gala.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to supporting the development of business relationships and will make every effort to promote this aim when partnering with you in a sponsorship. Your firm will have top priority in terms of time, exposure, and opportunity before, during and after the events.\r\n\r\nSponsorship options include: the highest-profile and sector-Exclusive <strong>Premier</strong> Sponsorship; <strong>Associate</strong> Sponsorship (includes a Table-for-10), individual <strong>Awards</strong> Sponsorships (2 tickets to attend + strong Logo branding and Introduction on Stage at Gala), “Break-out Sessions”, or bespoke Sponsorships based on your needs.\r\n\r\nAll Sponsorship packages include a mix of pre-Event, Event, and post-Event promotion and PR, via multiple media channels and a multitude of media partners. We are also increasingly present on social media, including LinkedIn, Twitter, YouTube and Facebook.\r\n\r\n<strong>To get more information, contact Thom Barnhardt at: tb(at)ceecapitalmarketsawards.com, or call +48 508 143 963; or 48-22-831-7062. </strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3> <a href="http://www.obligacje.pl/"><img class=" wp-image-257 alignleft" src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/obligacje.png" alt="" width="203" height="90" /></a> <a href="https://www.analizy.pl/"><img class=" wp-image-258 alignleft" src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-cont