(210, 1, '2018-03-12 10:26:58', '2018-03-12 10:26:58', '<strong>Head of Finance Management Institute\r\nPresident CFA Society Poland Professor of Economic Sciences at Wroclaw University of Economics</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTitle given by the President of Poland in 1992. He is a member in supervisory board in the past and at present in several enterprises and financial institutions, including Warsaw Stock Exchange. He cooperates in the form of training, consulting and expertise in the area of corporate finance, financial market, investment, risk management, banking and real estate with the following institutions: Commission of Supervisory of Insurance Companies and Pension Funds, National Bank of Poland, Polish Bankers Association, Warsaw Stock Exchange, National Securities Depository, Securities and Exchange Commission, some financial institutions and some enterprises.', 'Krzysztof Jajuga', 'President CFA Society Poland Professor of Economic Sciences at Wroclaw University of Economics\r\n\r\nHead of Finance Management Institute', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'krzysztof-jajuga', '', '', '2018-03-12 10:26:58', '2018-03-12 10:26:58', '', 0, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/?post_type=team&#038;p=210', 0, 'team', '', 0),
