(212, 1, '2018-03-12 10:28:16', '2018-03-12 10:28:16', '<strong>Chairman of Polish Associations of Brokers and Investment Advisors </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nChairman of Polish Associations of Brokers and Investment Advisors (ZMID). Holder of stock broker license issued by Polish Financial Supervision Authority in 2007 and CFA Charterholder since 2013. Frequent guest in TV and radio programs with his commentaries concerning global and local economy. Seven years of experience as a lecturer in a self-owned company providing professional financial trainings for brokers, analysts and private clients. Moreover, author and presenter of “DNA Rynkow” - weekly economic presentation about what is important for investors and what is happening on the markets ( <a href="http://dnarynkow.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">dnarynkow.com</a> )', 'Pawel Cymcyk', 'Chairman of Polish Associations of Brokers and Investment Advisors ', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'pawel-cymcyk', '', '', '2018-03-12 10:28:16', '2018-03-12 10:28:16', '', 0, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/?post_type=team&#038;p=212', 0, 'team', '', 0),
