(230, 1, '2018-03-12 10:36:46', '2018-03-12 10:36:46', '<strong>Bucharest Stock Exchange\r\nDirector, Investor Relations and Public Relations Department </strong>\r\n\r\nWith more than 10 years of experience on the Romanian capital markets, Daniela has been involved in the past years in the development and promotion of the market towards local and foreign communities. She is part of a team charged with the mission to implement a deep reform of the Romanian capital market, so as to gain by it the status of the Emerging Market and in view to transform Bucharest into the capital market hub of South-Eastern Europe. Holding the position of Director of Investor Relations and Public Relations Department within the Bucharest Stock Exchange (BVB) since 2015, contributed to increasing visibility of the market and implementing the most extensive and diverse program in Eastern Europe aimed at building up the equities culture, strengthening corporate governance compliance and enhancing financial education among investors and entrepreneurs. Daniela started working with the Bucharest Stock Exchange 5 years ago, as an advisor to the CEO, being involved over time in various areas within the company, such as Financial Reporting and Analysis, Communication, Investor Relations, Corporate Governance and Indices management. Before joining BVB, Daniela was a financial markets editor and presenter at the economic TV station in Romania for 2 years, after working for 3 years as a stockbroker.', 'Daniela Serban', 'Director, Investor Relations and Public Relations Department\r\n\r\nBucharest Stock Exchange', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'daniela-serban', '', '', '2018-03-12 10:37:04', '2018-03-12 10:37:04', '', 0, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/?post_type=team&#038;p=230', 0, 'team', '', 0),
