(252, 1, '2018-03-12 11:40:40', '2018-03-12 11:40:40', '<h1>Matchmaking/Connect Summit</h1>\n<h3><b>CEE Capital Markets Connect Summit – 12 September 2018</b></h3>\n<span style="font-size: medium;">The aim of the <b>CEE Capital Markets Connect Summit</b> is to connect Great Companies with smart Institutional Investors. </span>\n\n<span style="font-size: medium;">In 2018, we are expanding our Summit and Awards in 2 directions:</span>\n\n<span style="font-size: medium;">a) We will include not only </span><span style="font-size: medium;"><b>publicly-traded companies but also private companies backed by PE/VCs</b></span><span style="font-size: medium;"> and promising young companies with high-growt</span>h potential. These companies will be from a wide range of sectors, from FinTech to xTech and old-economy companies.\n\nb) <b>Matching Investors with Companies</b>. Our aim is to connect Great Companies with Smart Money, focusing on 3 stages in a company''s capital raising life-cycle: Start-Ups; Expansion Stage; and Undiscovered Gems. The aim of the <b>CEE Capital Markets Connect Summit</b> is to connect Great Companies with Smart Institutional Investors.\n\n8:00– 9:15 <b>Registration and VIP Breakfast </b>\n\n9:15 – 9:45 <b>Opening KeyNote Address: How CEE''s Companies and Capital Markets are battling to the top of the world''s stage.</b>\n\n9:30 – 10:15 <b>VIP Panel:</b> <b>Raising capital in CEE – versus non-CEE options</b>: Capital knows no borders, and companies have a multitude of capital raising options. While CEE markets remain the leading choice, other options include non-public/PE investors from places like Silicon Valley or Israel, and non-traditional public exchanges such as South Africa, Scandinavia, London or the U.S.\n\n10:15 – 10:45 <b>Coffee and Networking</b>\n\n10:45 – 12:30 <b>Break-out Sessions/Matchmaking</b>:\n\na) <b>StartUp Pitches: 25 brilliant or brash business ideas</b> (for those looking for 100,000 euro to 500,000 euro). Company must be pre-qualified (via website application). Limited to <b>10</b> minutes.\n\nb) “<b>Expansion or Next Stage</b>”:<b> 15 revenue-generating companies in next stage of financing</b> (Euro 500,000 -5,000,000). Company must be pre-qualified (via website application). Limited to <b>15</b> minutes.\n\nc) “<b>Undiscovered Gems</b>” – <b>9</b> Publicly-listed companies set for rapid growth, unanticipated profitability, or exceptional capital gains. Top companies from different sectors present their case. Disruptive business models, unique advantages of CEE-based companies, and overlooked niches in CEE. (Company must be approved by our Investment Partners.) Limited to <b>25</b> minutes.\n\n12:30 – 14:00 <b>VIP Networking Luncheon</b>\n\n<span style="font-size: medium;">The Summit concludes at 14:00 and is followed by the evening </span><span style="font-size: medium;"><b>CEE Capital Markets Connect Awards Gala</b></span><span style="font-size: medium;">, beginning at 18:30. </span>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Summit', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-03-12 11:40:40', '2018-03-12 11:40:40', '', 17, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/2018/03/12/17-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
