(277, 1, '2018-03-13 07:11:32', '2018-03-13 07:11:32', '<h3>19 Winners announced at CEE Capital Markets Awards</h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h4><b>CEE Capital Markets Awards distinguishes top public companies listed in Central Eastern Europe</b></h4>\n&nbsp;\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-286 aligncenter" src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_WinnersGroupmailingSavvy_400px-1.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n&nbsp;\n\nThe 3rd annual <b>CEE Capital Markets Awards Gala</b> was held yesterday (13 September, 2017) at the InterContinental Hotel in Warsaw, Poland, attracting more than 100 VIPs from the Capital Markets sector. The Awards distinguished publicly-listed companies who are leading the dynamic and fast-paced changes in the CEE region. Nominations were received from Poland, Romania, Ukraine, Hungary, Czech Republic, and Lithuania.\n\nIn addition to the final Short-List of 71 leading companies who competed for the top-prize in 19 categories, 5 CEE-region Stock Exchanges attended, including <b>Warsaw Stock Exchange, Bucharest Stock Exchange, Prague and CEE Stock Exchange</b> and <b>NASDAQ. </b>\n\nInternational guests attending were from UK, USA, Finland, Sweden, Israel, India, Ireland, Romania, Hungary, Czech Republic, Slovakia, and Switzerland.\n\n“We have 3 main goals in organizing this Awards”, said <b>Thom Barnhardt</b>, organizer of this annual CEE Capital Markets Awards. “First, we want to encourage more global investor attention on the CEE region - stretching from the Baltics to the Black Sea – with its more-dynamic economies than western Europe - to attract more global investors to the region''s great companies. Secondly, we want to highlight top entrepreneurs and managers creating and building great companies.” The third goal, according to Barnhardt, is to shine a light on top institutional investors. “Especially those doing the extra work to discover rising stars in the region.”\n<h3>The 19 CEE Capital Markets Awards winners are:</h3>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top IPO</h5>\nDino Polska S.A.\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DINO_logo_web_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top Secondary Listing</h5>\nFamur S.A.\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Secondary_FamurmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top CEE Company Listed on non-CEE Stock Exchange</h5>\nMedicover AB\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Medicover-Top-CEE-based-company-Listing-outside-CEEmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top Performing (Percentage return)</h5>\nMedLife\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Performing_MedlifemailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Best IR dept of a listed company – CEE</h5>\nBucharest Stock Exchange\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_IR_CEE_Bucharest_SEmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Best IR dept of a listed company – Poland</h5>\nCyfrowy Polsat SA\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_IR_Poland-Cyfrowy-PolsatmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top Bond listing deal of Year</h5>\nGlobe Trade Centre SA\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Erez-GTC-Top-Bond-Listing-mailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Turnaround of the Year</h5>\nGlobe Trade Centre SA\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_GTC-Erez-Turnaround-of-the-YearmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Small Cap/Lightly-Regulated Exchanges (New Connect; AeRO): Listing of Year – SmallCap</h5>\nNestmedic\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_NestmedicmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Performer of Year – SmallCap</h5>\nGLG Pharma S.A.\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_GLGmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Best Transition-to-Main Market (Small Cap to Main Market):</h5>\nUnimot S.A.\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Piotr-Unimot.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top M&amp;A Deal of the Year</h5>\nFAMUR buys Kopex\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_FamurmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Best overall company of the Year – CEE</h5>\nMedLife\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Overall-Company_CEE_MedlifemailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Best overall company of the Year – Poland</h5>\nCyfrowy Polsat SA\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Overall-Company_Poland_CyfrowymailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Investors: Top Fund of the Year – Domestic</h5>\nAviva Investors Akcyjny SFIO\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Aviva_web_logo.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top foreign institutional/ pension investor in CEE</h5>\nTrigon New Europe Fund C Unit\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Fund_CEE_TrigonmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Service Providers: Top Broker/Investment Bank for CEE</h5>\nPKO Bank Polski SA brokerage\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Top-Broker_PKOmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top Law Firm</h5>\nWhite &amp; Case M. Studniarek i Wspólnicy\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Law_WhitemailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="winner_box">\n<h5>Top IR company of year</h5>\nCC Group sp. z o.o.\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_IR-of-Year_CC-GroupmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" />\n\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n', 'Winner 2017', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-03-13 07:11:32', '2018-03-13 07:11:32', '', 23, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/2018/03/12/23-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
