in the region.”\r\n\r\n<h3>The 19 CEE Capital Markets Awards winners are:</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="winner_box">\r\n<h5>Top IPO</h5><br/>\r\nDino Polska S.A. <br/>\r\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DINO_logo_web_400px.jpg">\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n<div class="winner_box">\r\n<h5>Top Secondary Listing </h5><br/>\r\nFamur S.A. <br/>\r\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Secondary_FamurmailingSavvy_400px.jpg">\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n<div class="winner_box">\r\n<h5>Top CEE Company Listed on non-CEE Stock Exchange</h5><br/>\r\nMedicover AB <br/>\r\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Secondary_FamurmailingSavvy_400px.jpg">\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n<div class="winner_box">\r\n<h5>Top Performing (Percentage return) </h5><br/>\r\nMedLife <br/>\r\n<img src="http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ceeCMA17_Winner_Secondary_FamurmailingSavvy_400px.jpg">\r\n </div>', 'Winner 2017', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-13 06:40:03', '2018-03-13 06:40:03', '', 23, 'http://bectortechnologies.com/ccedesign/2018/03/13/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
