and</h3>\r\n<h4>Cyfrowy Polsat SA</h4>\r\n<img src="http://ceecapitalmarketsawards.com/images/gallery/2017/winners-small/ceeCMA17_Winner_Overall Company_Poland_CyfrowymailingSavvy_400px.jpg" alt="" /></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="list-style-type: none">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Investors: Top Fund of the Year – Domestic</h3>\r\n<h4>Aviva Investors Akcyjny SFIO</h4>\r\n<img src="http://ceecapitalmarketsawards.com/images/gallery/2017/winners-small/Aviva_web_logo.jpg" alt="" /></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="list-style-type: none">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Top foreign institutional/ pension investor in CEE</h3>\r\n<h4>Trigon New Europe Fund C Unit</h4>\r\n<img src="http://ceecapitalmarketsawards.com/images/gallery/2017/winners-small/ceeCMA17_Winner_Fund_CEE_TrigonmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" alt="" /></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="list-style-type: none">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Service Providers: Top Broker/Investment Bank for CEE</h3>\r\n<h4>PKO Bank Polski SA brokerage</h4>\r\n<img src="http://ceecapitalmarketsawards.com/images/gallery/2017/winners-small/ceeCMA17_Winner_Top Broker_PKOmailingSavvy_400px.jpg" alt="" /></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="list-style-type: none">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Top Law Firm</h3>\r\n<h4>White &amp; Case M. Studniarek i Wspólnicy</h4>\r\n<img src="http://ceecapitalmarketsawards.com/images/gallery/2017/winners-small/ceeCMA17_Winner_Law_WhitemailingSavvy_400px.jpg" alt="" /></div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style="list-style-type: none">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Top IR company of year</h3>\r\n<h4>CC Group sp. z o.o.</h4